In Ex. 4., pag. 26. y^{2}\dot{x}^{2}-3x^{2}\dot{x}\dot{y}+2x^{2}\dot{x}^{2}-ax\dot{y}{2}+a^{2}\dot{x}^{2}=0 radix y est =

x+Bx^{\frac{2}{3}}-BBx^{\frac{1}{3}}+\overline{\frac{a}{2}+B^{3}}\cdot x^{0}+\frac{1}{9}\overline{aB-B^{4}}\cdot x^{-\frac{1}{3}}+\overline{\frac{5}{36} aBB+B^{5}}\cdot x^{-\frac{2}{3}}-\overline{\frac{aa}{4}-\frac{3}{10}aB^{3}-B^{6}}x+Bx^{\frac{2}{3}}-BBx^{\frac{1}{3}}+\left(\frac{a}{2}+B^{3}\right)x^{0}+\frac{1}{9}\left(aB-B^{4}\right)x^{-\frac{1}{3}}+\left(\frac{5}{36} aBB+B^{5}\right)x^{-\frac{2}{3}}-\left(\frac{aa}{4}-\frac{3}{10}aB^{3}-B^{6}\right)


\cdot x^{-1}+\overline{\frac{17}{324}aaB+\frac{73}{180}aB^{4}+B^{7}}x^{-\frac{4}{3}}\text{ \&c.}x^{-1}+\left(\frac{17}{324}aaB+\frac{73}{180}aB^{4}+B^{7}\right)x^{-\frac{4}{3}}\text{ etc.} item y=2x+a-\frac{2aa}{7}x^{-1}+\frac{6a^{3}}{35}x^{-2}-\frac{88a^{4}}{637}x^{-3}\text{  \&c}y=2x+a-\frac{2aa}{7}x^{-1}+\frac{6a^{3}}{35}x^{-2}-\frac{88a^{4}}{637}x^{-3}\text{  etc.};
